"A, A Decepticon" Stammers Drag Strip, "No way, no way, no way" blurts
Speedbreaker. Motormaster walks towards him, with his gun down non
threatenignly. "I thought all the Decepticons were scraped by the Predacons
after the cybertronian war" he stated in discust. "But if you are a
Decepticon warrior, and you want to have what we once had, then Welcome to
the DECEPTICON EMPIRE" he finishes, extending his hand.
